### 🧪 Security HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# =========================================================================
# 1. SQL INJECTION PREVENTION TEST
# =========================================================================

# 1.1. Search Safe (Aman dari SQL Injection karena parameterized)
GET {{host}}/api/security/sql-safe?name=iPhone

###

# 1.2. Search Raw Safe (Aman menggunakan interpolation)
GET {{host}}/api/security/sql-raw-safe?name=Samsung

###

# =========================================================================
# 2. XSS (CROSS-SITE SCRIPTING) PREVENTION TEST
# =========================================================================

# 2.1. Kirim input script XSS berbahaya (Akan disanitasi)
POST {{host}}/api/security/xss-sanitize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "<script>alert('Hacked!');</script> Halo teman-teman!"
}

###

# =========================================================================
# 3. RATE LIMITING TEST
# =========================================================================
# Eksekusi request ini secara cepat berturut-turut (> 5x dalam 10 detik).
# Request ke-6 akan menghasilkan: 429 Too Many Requests.
GET {{host}}/api/security/rate-limited
